      <title>随着廉价市场重新开放，土耳其搁置了具有里程碑意义的阿联酋伊斯兰债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/turkey-shelves-landmark-uae-sukuk-deal-as-cheaper-markets-reopen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其暂停了与阿拉伯联合酋长国的 85 亿美元伊斯兰债券交易，在全球债券市场探索更便宜的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/turkey-shelves-landmark-uae-sukuk-deal-as-cheaper-markets-reopen</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 11:04:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国央行表示，德国经济衰退并不意味着经济严重下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/german-recession-doesn-t-mean-severe-downturn-bundesbank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行表示，即使德国经济目前可能陷入衰退，但它并未面临严重衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/german-recession-doesn-t-mean-severe-downturn-bundesbank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>推动改革后阿联酋准备退出监管机构的黑钱名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/uae-abu-dhabi-dubai-poised-to-exit-watchdog-fatf-s-dirty-money-gray-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在努力打击进出这个石油资源丰富的海湾国家的非法资金流动之后，阿拉伯联合酋长国预计最早将于本周退出全球监管机构的“灰名单”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/uae-abu-dhabi-dubai-poised-to-exit-watchdog-fatf-s-dirty-money-gray-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:53:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲碳排放量下降 5% 至两年多来最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/european-carbon-slumps-5-to-lowest-in-more-than-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于天然气价格下跌、气候温和以及可再生能源产量飙升，削弱了污染许可证的需求，欧洲碳排放量两年多来首次跌破每吨 55 欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/european-carbon-slumps-5-to-lowest-in-more-than-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:42:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷和赛勒斯计划收购伦敦绍森德机场以结束债务纠纷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/carlyle-cyrus-plan-london-southend-airport-takeover-to-end-debt-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦绍森德机场已与债权人凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group) 和赛勒斯资本合伙人 (Cyrus Capital Partners) 就债务重组达成一致，这两家公司将接管该公司，以换取提供新的融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/carlyle-cyrus-plan-london-southend-airport-takeover-to-end-debt-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:09:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国和德国提议减少损害增长的欧盟规范</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/france-and-germany-to-propose-reducing-eu-norms-that-hurt-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，他将在三月初与德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克提出建议，以减少他认为阻碍企业发展并损害经济增长的欧盟规范。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/france-and-germany-to-propose-reducing-eu-norms-that-hurt-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:02:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美今年可能出售债券，重点关注期限较长的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/aramco-may-sell-bonds-this-year-with-focus-on-long-maturities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司财务主管表示，随着金融市场有所改善，该公司今年可能会出售债券，并且该公司希望出售长期债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/aramco-may-sell-bonds-this-year-with-focus-on-long-maturities</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:50:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装红海导弹袭击后船员弃船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/houthi-hit-ship-rubymar-was-struck-in-engine-room-manager-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘商船在红海南部遭到导弹袭击后，船员抛弃了这艘船。几个月来，胡塞武装分子一直威胁那里的贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/houthi-hit-ship-rubymar-was-struck-in-engine-room-manager-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 08:02:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多金属集团将退出俄罗斯十大金矿开采商行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/gold-miner-polymetal-to-sell-russian-unit-for-3-7-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年因入侵乌克兰而受到美国制裁的俄罗斯业务出售后，多金属国际公司将不再跻身全球产量前十名金矿商之列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/gold-miner-polymetal-to-sell-russian-unit-for-3-7-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 05:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对需求的担忧挥之不去，油价从三周高点下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对需求前景的持续担忧抵消了中东持续的紧张局势，油价从三周以来的最高水平下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 23:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
